Nobody is going to give you anything you have to take it The truth is ugly but the truth discussed is beautiful. It will hurt some feelings and bruise some egos. Listening to the truth told in this Episode of Shop Talk titled Age discrimination will be almost cathartic. The host Adefarasin discusses with such brilliance and understanding, age discrimination, alongside Fela Durotoye, Seyi Babatope, Diipo Ayo-Adeusi and the host, Adeolu Adefarasin. The experience is best experienced than narrated. Click on the video below to view the full episode of Shop Talk: 